 inappropriate external links and by adding encyclopedic content written from a neutral point of view december  learn how and when to remove this template message broadsoft inc type public traded as nasdaq bsft industry communication software founded   years ago  headquarters gaithersburg maryland united states revenue  millionas of update website httpwwwbroadsoftcom broadsoft inc nasdaq bsft is a global communication software and service provider with over  customers worldwide supporting millions of subscribers the company provides cloudbased unified communications solutions to communications service providers based on their ucone solution which consists of two product platforms broadworks and broadcloud  in  the company acquired the british company hosted ip communications europe ltd hipcom and the german company finocom ag both providers of clouddelivered unified communications services contents  background  awards  references  external links backgroundedit the company was founded by michael tessler and scott d hoffpauir in  the products and services of the company play a critical part in the network by serving as the software which delivers and coordinates call control and information transmission over service providers’ ipbased network its products include broadworks and broadcloud the company’s flagship product broadworks is a voice over internet protocol voip applications platform that enables service providers to deliver basic and enhanced voice services for business and residential end users  see more at httpwwwbroadsoftcomserviceprovidersproductsapplicationsbroadworkssthashbkrnlwtdpuf broadcloud is a fully managed service that delivers broadsoft’s comprehensive unified communications services  see more at httpwwwbroadsoftcomserviceprovidersproductsapplicationsbroadcloudsthashqiugdpuf in  the company was selected as the supplier of sprint corporation nasdaq s for its next generation multimedia systembased network and volte development on may   broadsoft inc announced the acquisition of reston virginiabased intellinote an enterprise messagingbased team communication and collaboration software application built for the increasingly mobile and millennial workforce awardsedit in  the company received frost  sullivan  new product innovation leadership award for its hosted unified communication platform product in the same year thanks to its unified communication platform ucone it won the peoples choice stevie award in the th american business award competition ucone was listed in favorite telecommunications service list referencesedit  a b bsft key statistics  broadsoft inc stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom retrieved    bsft profile broadsoft inc stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom retrieved    a b broadsoft inc bsftoq quote reuterscom reuterscom retrieved    sprint taps broadsoft for volte transition lightreadingcom retrieved    broadsoft inc nasdaq bsft quotes  news  google finance googlecom retrieved    flook bill  augiust  broadsoft buys hipcom in uk expansion washington business journal retrieved  april   broadsoft inc bsft marketwatch marketwatchcom retrieved    broadsoft inc bsft earnings report date  nasdaqcom nasdaqcom retrieved    sprint selects broadsoft to deliver nextgeneration ims and voice over lte services sgfinanceyahoocom  retrieved    broadsoft announces acquisition of intellinote press release broadsoft  may    broadsoft receives frost  sullivan  new product innovation leadership award broadsoftcom  retrieved    broadsoft wins peoples choice stevier award in  american business awardsm competition financeyahoocom  retrieved   external linksedit official corporate website official developer website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlebroadsoftoldid categories companies established in companies listed on nasdaqhidden categories articles with a promotional tone from december all articles with a promotional tonearticles containing potentially dated statements from all articles containing pote