osted ip communications europe ltd hipcom and the german company finocom ag both providers of clouddelivered unified communications services contents  background  awards  references  external links backgroundedit the company was founded by michael tessler and scott d hoffpauir in  the products and services of the company play a critical part in the network by serving as the software which delivers and coordinates call control and information transmission over service providers’ ipbased network its products include broadworks and broadcloud the company’s flagship product broadworks is a voice over internet protocol voip applications platform that enables service providers to deliver basic and enhanced voice services for business and residential end users  see more at httpwwwbroadsoftcomserviceprovidersproductsapplicationsbroadworkssthashbkrnlwtdpuf broadcloud is a fully managed service that delivers broadsoft’s comprehensive unified communications services  see more at httpwwwbroadsoftcomserviceprovidersproductsapplicationsbroadcloudsthashqiugdpuf in  the company was selected as the supplier of sprint corporation nasdaq s for its next generation multimedia systembased network and volte development on may   broadsoft inc announced the acquisition of reston virginiabased intellinote an enterprise messagingbased team communication and collaboration software application built for the increasingly mobile and millennial workforce awardsedit in  the company received frost  sullivan  new product innovation leadership award for its hosted unified communication platform product in the same year thanks to its unified communication platform ucone it won the peoples choice stevie award in the th american business award competition ucone was listed in favorite telecommunications service list referencesedit  a b bsft key statistics  broadsoft inc stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom retrieved    bsft profile broadsoft inc stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom retrieved    a b broads