s  see more at httpwwwbroadsoftcomserviceprovidersproductsapplicationsbroadworkssthashbkrnlwtdpuf broadcloud is a fully managed service that delivers broadsoft’s comprehensive unified communications services  see more at httpwwwbroadsoftcomserviceprovidersproductsapplicationsbroadcloudsthashqiugdpuf in  the company was selected as the supplier of sprint corporation nasdaq s for its next generation multimedia systembased network and volte development on may   broadsoft inc announced the acquisition of reston virginiabased intellinote an enterprise messagingbased team communication and collaboration software application built for the increasingly mobile and millennial workforce awardsedit in  the company received frost  sullivan  new product innovation leadership award for its hosted unified communication platform product in the same year thanks to its unified communication platform ucone it won the peoples choice stevie award in the th american business award competition ucone was listed in favorite telecommunications service list referencesedit  a b bsft key statistics  broadsoft inc stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom retrieved    bsft profile broadsoft inc stock  yahoo finance financeyahoocom retrieved    a b broadsoft inc bsftoq quote reuterscom reuterscom retrieved    sprint taps broadsoft for volte transition lightreadingcom retrieved    broadsoft inc nasdaq bsft quotes  news  google finance googlecom retrieved    flook bill  augiust  broadsoft buys hipcom in uk expansion washington business journal retrieved  april   broadsoft inc bsft marketwatch marketwatchcom retrieved    broadsoft inc bsft earnings report date  nasdaqcom nasdaqcom retrieved    sprint selects broadsoft to deliver nextgeneration ims and voice over lte services sgfinanceyahoocom  retrieved    broadsoft announces acquisition of intellinote press release broadsoft  may    broadsoft receives frost  sullivan  new product innovation leadership award broadsoftcom  retrieved    broadsoft wins peopl