tuguese dutch mandarin arabic hebrew persian turkish greek flemish hindi romanian bulgarian finnish italian russian polish japanese czech and many others with all their beautiful dialects and flavors  we are natives we are immigrants our diversity is our strength and our corporate culture is grounded on common values as responsible global citizens our passion is to innovate to enable the human touch via communications and collaboration empowering people teams and companies to remove borders barriers walls and silos  we are one family broadsoft  our missionand vision   as a trusted cloud innovator and market leader we have continuously innovated in cloud unified communication software and services for the last  years — and we can’t stop committed to redefining the future of work by inspiring teams to create collaborate and perform in ways never before imagined our mission is to bring bestinclass productivity and collaboration tools to businesses broadsoft business provides a comprehensive mobileintegrated and completely open communication suite for businesses with carrierclass reliability and security by using our technology inspired by users and teams you can collaborate and communicate more effectively to make your work — simple our market leadership with  market share we are the industry leader for cloud unified communications with a secure and trusted platform chosen by  of the world’s top  service providers across  countries our proven portfolio the strength of our innovative technology and robust awardwinning portfolio has been recognized by industry pundits from all across the unified communications ecosystem broadsoft’s  share of the global hosted ip telephony and ucc services market confirms their leadership position elka popova industry director unified communications and collaboration frost  sullivan broadsoft presently has a clear edge over microsoft when it comes to cloud voice capabilities thirdparty integration mobility and contact center capabilities when considering voice capability it is clear that broadsoft’s long history of providing carriergrade voice functionality provides a service that is far more robust than microsoft’s cloud pbx with pstn connectivity e brent kelly presidentprincipal analyst kelcor inc it gives me great pleasure to honor broadsoft as a  recipient of tmc’s unified communications product of the year award for their innovative product broadcloud ucone our judges were very impressed with the ingenuity and excellence displayed by broadsoft in their groundbreaking work on broadcloud ucone rich tehrani ceo tmc broadsoft teamone continues to demonstrate product excellence with its comprehensive solution updated with integrations with different bestinclass business apps popular cloudbased file storage services and a powerful realtime videoaudiomessaging function  excellence in technology award winner  broadsoft teamone formerly intellinote frost  sullivan broadsoft ccone has a strong ability to analyze and leverage structured and unstructured enterprise data to support businessintelligencedriven contact routing decisions in real time a simple example is its ability to prioritize calls from customers who previously abandoned a call while waiting in queues  magic quadrant “visionary” placement for ccaas north america  broadsoft ccone formerly transera gartner the broadsoft ucaas consolidation play as practiced by vonage is beneficial to the industry as it builds brand awareness and scaling market trends five key trends in the shifting ucaas delivery landscape october  gartner our subsidiaries placetel is a leading cloud pbx provider and a whollyowned subsidiary of broadsoft based out of cologne germany placetel’s awardwinning telephone system is primarily aimed at small and midsize businesses and contains more than  powerful features that can be managed flexibly more than  customers have already opted for a cloud pbx solution from placetel broadsoft japan kk is a pioneer in creating innovative cloudbased communication solutions in japan and a whollyowned subsidiary of broadsoft based out of tokyo japan it provides hosted uc services that service providers deliver to the japanese market of  million small businesses — over  of japan’s work force helpful links leadership investor relations careers company broadsoft overview leadership investor relations awards press releases news events collateral careers office locations pledge of presence contact us solutions businesses government hospitality education service providers products broadsoft business ucone teamone ccone hub broadworks broadcloud broadsoft mobility services broadsoft design professional services training and certification customer support compliance privacy policy terms of service iso  tl   broadsoft all rights reserved follow us broadsoft  inc competitors and products in the call center marketplace  call center marketplacebroadsoft  incbroadsoft  inc rating   write a review  perry parkwaygaithersburg md about broadsoft  incbroadworks is a softwarebased hosted communications platform with a standardsbased modular architecture that provides the voice applications including hosted pbx ip centrex voice vpn and collaborative conferencing broadworks operates on open standards including session interface protocol sipcompetitors of broadsoft  incthe taylor reach group incthe taylor reach group is a call center and contact center consultant company specializing in customer experience consulting call and contact center consulting management performance technologies site selection tools and assessments the taylor reach group consultants each with more read more send an email email sent  products write a reviewarca technologies ltdintegrated voip and tdm platform providing bulk call generation protocol analysis and qos measurements read more send an email email sent write a reviewzultys incthe mx enterprise media exchange integrates voice data fax and video into a compact u box with a single user interface